description: Goh`s Dustox are the evolved form of Goh`s Cascoon. All three of his Cascoon evolved into Dustox after at the Sakuragi Institute bio-dome. They were spun up in a tree when all of Goh`s Pokémon were fighting over food and it flooded the dome, endangering them from evolving but the Pokémon worked together to protect Goh`s Cascoon so they could evolve.
name: Dokucale (Gou)
